                  <a class="services-icon" href="#">
                    <i class="fa fa-volume-up"></i>
                  </a>
                  <h4>Audio Chat</h4>
                  <p>
                    If you prefer to listen and speak instead of typing or video chat then audio chat will provide for
                    you.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <!-- end about-details -->
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-4 col-sm-4 col-xs-12">
            <!-- end col-md-4 -->
            <div class=" about-move">
              <div class="services-details">
                <div class="single-services">
                  <a class="services-icon" href="#">
                    <i class="fa fa-link"></i>
                  </a>
                  <h4>Resources Page </h4>
                  <p>
                    Resources page is a collection of links to topics related to mental health or other life issues. If
                    you want to learn more
                    about the different types of information related about mental health and suicide then you can visit
                    our resources page.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <!-- end about-details -->
            </div>
          </div>
          <!-- End Left services -->
          <div class="col-md-4 col-sm-4 col-xs-12">
            <!-- end col-md-4 -->
            <div class=" about-move">
              <div class="services-details">
                <div class="single-services">
                  <a class="services-icon" href="#">
                    <i class="fa fa-window-restore"></i>
                  </a>
                  <h4>Community Page</h4>
                  <p>
                    Community page is a collection of links to other organizations that provide a similar cause to ours
